{"pageProps":{"title":"2022 年常中集训游记 - 宝硕博客","post":{"title":"2022 年常中集训游记","excerpt":"这是我第一次出省参加外校集训。此行的目的地是江苏省常州高级中学，于 1907 年建校，截止本文写作时该校在「OIerDb 全国信息学竞赛学校排行榜」上位列第九。","content":[{"tag":"p","content":["这是我第一次出省参加外校集训。此行的目的地是江苏省常州高级中学，于 1907 年建校，截止本文写作时该校在「OIerDb 全国信息学竞赛学校排行榜」上位列第九。"]},{"tag":"span","attrs":{"id":"more"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"启程"},"content":["启程"]},{"tag":"p","content":["走前 2 天，也就是 2 月 18 日，我们才正式确定要动身去常中参加集训，当时火车票余票已经所剩无几了，索性直接买了一等座，省时省力，就是有点费钱。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/ys2OdY56rtDC43U.jpg","width":"51.25%","style":"margin-right:4px"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/JzSrD97LyP4KI8b.jpg","width":"45%"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["一等座确实比二等座舒服了很多，还有免费的零食、饮料、矿泉水。不过，要是下次可以自己挑的话，我还是选二等座，经济实惠。"]},{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/AnK1PqdCfQHEcYj.jpg","width":"300","style":"display:block;margin:0 auto 1rem"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"p","content":["晚饭在火车上买了份「豚骨面」，花了 39 元，除了汤有点发酸（可能是醋倒多了）以外别的没啥毛病。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"见闻"},"content":["见闻"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"住宿"},"content":["住宿"]},{"tag":"p","content":["由于学校没有给我们提供宿舍，所以我们两人成团一起住宾馆，每间 160 元/晚。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/vbwahiHPXu7IU21.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["环境还行，凑合着住。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"食堂"},"content":["食堂"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/YgAPOB6K7xFnwJI.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["▲ 外景"]},{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/27/xaUc8KZ1WICibop.jpg","width":"300","style":"display:block;margin:0 auto 1rem"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"p","content":["▲ 饭卡"]},{"tag":"p","content":["食堂的餐食比假期的二南好多了，但我觉得赶不上开学时候的二南食堂。"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"蹭网"},"content":["蹭网"]},{"tag":"p","content":["常中并没有给我们分配上网账号，所以要么用打开文件资源管理器都能死机的台式机上网，要么用自己的笔记本离线操作。"]},{"tag":"p","content":["毛主席说过：「自己动手，丰衣足食。」所以我们把台式机的网线拔下来插到了自己的电脑上，并且手动配好了 IP 地址，成功解决了上网问题。"]},{"tag":"p","content":["蹭网期间出一个小插曲：有人拿自己配好的网开热点给大家共享网络，结果被系统自动断网并且封掉设备了…"]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"校园"},"content":["校园"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/LS9EumNvBynMIV5.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["进入校园。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/5K2pODGQ1U3ufhF.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["标志性的「",{"tag":"strong","content":["SCZ"]},"」标识。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/RYWTNgijmfVn6H2.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["校园一角。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/wF9MVZO6W21rvnp.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"p","content":["教学楼外景。"]},{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/vqHWncS4VOZ6Rhd.jpg","height":"450"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"p","content":["小亭子。"]},{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/r7RFDVZcCAPuoNx.jpg","width":"48%","style":"margin-right:4px"},"content":[""]}," ",{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/RYzfbEPtmDBk6F9.jpg","width":"48%"},"content":[""]},{"tag":"p","content":["学校旁边的 ",{"tag":"a","attrs":{"href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%81%E5%AE%9D%E5%A1%94","rel":"external nofollow noreferrer"},"content":["天宁宝塔"]},"。"]},{"tag":"h2","attrs":{"id":"返程"},"content":["返程"]},{"tag":"p","content":["来的时候在火车上吃的是面条，于是返程的时候买了一盒「红烧牛肉饭」，花了 40 元，味道也不错。"]},{"tag":"p","content":[{"tag":"img","attrs":{"src":"https://s1.baoshuo.ren/2022/02/28/4pWTVO6eE1UBwKk.jpg","alt":"","loading":"lazy"},"content":[""]}]},{"tag":"h3","attrs":{"id":"花絮"},"content":["花絮"]},{"tag":"p","content":["回学校的